Changes for 0.4.4 (2025-10-31)
  * Updated html reporting to support more cases
Changes for 0.4.3 (2025-10-31)
  * Bug fixes
Changes for 0.4.0 (2025-09-17)
  * Logging Clang Diagnostics, ClangTool and tool specific logs to a common file.
  * Enabled only user facing prints to terminal.
  * Skipping structs with constructors in it.

Changes for 0.3.0 (2025-09-12)
  * Fixed bugs related to typedefs and anonymous types.
  * Redesigned command-line options for the binary.
  * Structured output reports and updated unit test cases.

Changes for 0.2.0 (2025-09-07)
  * Removed support for typedefs and anonymous structs/enums/unions.

Changes for 0.1.0 (2025-09-02)
  * Initial release of clang-ast-based static header analysis tool.
  * Detects backward-incompatible changes in C/C++ public headers.
  * Includes basic CLI interface and HTML output formatting.
  * Designed for internal development and testing.
